	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just received a PowerPak for the 8-bit Nintendo system, and I'm wondering if anyone else has run into the same problem I'm facing. I have tried it with two different CF cards on two separate NES consoles, and each time I get the same result.<br /><br />The picture is doubled up, and the text appears garbled (O's end up being G's for some reason). Obviously, it is not useable. <br /><br />I've attached a picture of the startup screen.<br /><br />Anyone have some advice? I searched around on this forum, and couldn't find anything obvious that seemed related. Is my PowerPak defective?

		
