	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looks like something's wrong with PPU A6 or A7. (You're seeing &amp; instead of ., and patterns are repeating every 4 rows (or 128 tiles) ... I wouldn't be surprised if this is a connector problem rather than a powerpak problem, but there could be an incorrect solder blob on the powerpak.

		

